[This report provides a vivid account of the challenges in ensuring that viable vaccine reaches the arm of the individual in these campaigns. Lack of infrastructure is surely a major problem in Darfur. Should the campaign need to move into more remote areas, that challenge will become even greater. Little has been said about the armed conflict in the area, and how that is affecting the vaccination campaign. - Mod.TY

